history.proof: intros a b H. unfold quotient_euclide, remainder_euclide. hauto lq: on depth: 3.

exceptions.exn: In environment a, b : nat H : b <> 0 Unable to unify "b * (let (q, _) := euclide a b H in q) + (let (H, e0) := euclide a b H in let (r, _) := e0 in r)" with "a".

original: intros a b H. unfold quotient_euclide, remainder_euclide. reflexivity.
